ated electrical neurotransmission is conserved in the mammalian CN across echolocating bats and non-echolocating mice.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Accomando, Alyssa W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Johnson, Mark A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "McLaughlin, Madeline A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Simmons, James A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Simmons, Andrea Megela", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8f29f9f83ebf53baa350caf70ce62f3c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/2e32574a69fb2d4f1cfaf0cbb87d79c17391726f4838041d5e9467f0979474bd", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZLB43UPM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZLB43UPM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/738160e6b51c62359bbdf9d7e94aeae6!/b167999-170472", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "281-290", "title": "Journal of the Association for Research in Otolaryngology", "volume": "24"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8f29f9f83ebf53baa350caf70ce62f3c"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:ZLB43UPM"}, {"identifier": "10.1007/s10162-023-00898-y"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "ba